name: SalesListsOnline
overview:
SaleslistsOnline enables organizations to find their ideal business prospects and make fast, informed decisions to improve and personalize relationships with their customers. For over a decade, we have dominated the direct marketing industry. With our unsurpassed focus on customer care and our relentless dedication to provide only the finest, targeted data, we stand behind the effectiveness of our lists 100%. SaleslistsOnline has a knowledgeable group of professionals ready to assist you in selecting data of unmatched accuracy that is sure to vastly increase the probability of success with your project. Our proprietary analysis and enhancement processes are so vastly different from the compiled data available from other sources, that we guarantee the quality of our lists in writing.

Our superior list accuracy is the same reason why over 54% of SaleslistsOnline’s business consists of repeat orders.

SaleslistsOnline specializes in providing business and consumer mailing lists that are privacy-compliant, accurate and affordable. Our continuously updated direct mail lists allow you to target your market, grow your sales and increase your profits. The combination of quality data, superior customer service and impartial recommendations has made us the leading mailing list provider of choice for thousands of customers across the country.
